org.apache.ignite.ml.math

Interface MetaAttributes

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Matrix, NamedVector, Vector
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMatrix, AbstractVector, DelegatingNamedVector, DelegatingVector, DenseMatrix, DenseVector, SparseMatrix, SparseVector, VectorizedViewMatrix, VectorView, ViewMatrix

    public interface MetaAttributes
    Interface provides support for meta attributes on vectors and matrices.
